 "lrc": "[00:02.16]Yeah\n[00:02.16]Uh\n[00:05.20]Sun coming up like it knows something\n[00:08.96]This summer feel different already\n[00:10.72]Come on\n[00:13.04]Ooh, we been waiting on the light\n[00:20.80]Ooh, we gon’ get it right\n[00:24.80]Ooh, no more losing time\n[00:26.88]This summer, this summer\n[00:29.36]Same desk, same chair, same old ceiling\n[00:34.80]Boss man talking, but I lost that feeling\n[00:36.72]Two weeks off if the stars line up\n[00:38.48]But the flight costs more than the whole damn check\n[00:40.40]Everybody saying hold on, stay safe\n[00:42.56]Clock keep eating up another good day\n[00:44.40]I used to let July just slide right by\n[00:46.24]Like the sun was free but it wasn’t mine\n[00:48.24]Scrolling on the phone while the world got loud\n[00:50.32]Everybody building, I was sitting in doubt\n[00:52.00]Heard all that AI talk, thought it wasn’t for me\n[00:53.92]Now I’m looking at the wave like wait, that’s a key\n[00:55.84]No suitcase yet, but the plan got motion\n[00:58.00]Laptop open with a rum by the ocean\n[01:00.00]Not there now, but I see that scene\n[01:01.68]Gotta build that life before I live that dream\n[01:03.84]We don’t wanna waste no weather\n[01:05.92]We don’t wanna wait forever\n[01:09.20]One more spark and we come alive\n[01:12.48]One more step and we change the vibe\n[01:17.20]This summer gon’ be different\n[01:20.00]We ain’t letting it fade away\n[01:20.42]Got the sun on our shoulders\n[01:25.12]Got a brand new game to play\n[01:27.49]This summer gon’ be different\n[01:28.93]No more waiting on someday\n[01:30.88]We gon’ learn a little something\n[01:32.56]We gon’ build our own way\n[01:34.32]Pour it up, let it breathe\n[01:36.99]Palm trees in the fantasy\n[01:38.88]But we working while it glows\n[01:40.64]So the future feels easy\n[01:42.56]This summer gon’ be different\n[01:45.92]Different, different, different\n[01:46.72]This summer gon’ be different\n[01:46.72]And I’m different too\n[01:50.96]Na na na, we outside\n[01:53.44]But the mind on overdrive\n[01:55.47]Na na na, feel that heat\n[01:56.00]New world under my feet\n[01:56.00]I ain’t tryna be another tired face\n[02:07.20]Counting down Friday like an escape\n[02:08.64]I want Monday feeling like my own damn lane\n[02:10.80]Not a locked up loop with a different name\n[02:12.72]So I’m diving in, no perfect start\n[02:14.64]No fancy degree, just a hungry heart\n[02:16.56]Prompt by prompt, I’m learning the flow\n[02:18.56]Ask better questions, watch better doors show\n[02:20.72]Build me a bot, build me a site\n[02:22.56]Build me a plan for a better life\n[02:24.56]Automate the boring, sharpen the brain\n[02:26.40]Turn small sparks into summer rain\n[02:28.48]Everybody wants the beach with no pressure\n[02:30.08]Cold drink, clean sky, time you can measure\n[02:32.00]But that kind of peace don’t fall from blue\n[02:33.92]You gotta make the machine start working for you\n[02:35.92]Focus in the morning, rhythm at night\n[02:38.00]Discipline dancing with neon lights\n[02:39.92]Will in my chest, hunger in my shoes\n[02:41.76]This ain’t motivation, this is something to prove\n[02:44.40]We don’t wanna waste no weather\n[02:48.00]We don’t wanna wait forever\n[02:51.52]One more spark and we come alive\n[02:53.92]One more step and we change the vibe\n[02:58.72]This summer gon’ be different\n[03:00.80]We ain’t letting it fade away\n[03:03.84]Got the sun on our shoulders\n[03:05.52]Got a brand new game to play\n[03:07.13]This summer gon’ be different\n[03:08.51]No more waiting on someday\n[03:10.88]We gon’ learn a little something\n[03:13.28]We gon’ build our own way\n[03:15.36]Pour it up, let it breathe\n[03:17.28]Palm trees in the fantasy\n[03:19.20]But we working while it glows\n[03:20.88]So the future feels easy\n[03:22.64]This summer gon’ be different\n[03:25.28]Different, different, different\n[03:26.98]This summer gon’ be different\n[03:28.72]And I’m different too\n[03:30.32]Imagine no alarm with a panic in it\n[03:32.96]No boss in your head every single minute\n[03:34.69]Just waves, good friends, and the room to breathe\n[03:37.14]But first we plant the seed\n[03:38.87]Imagine that view with your name on it\n[03:41.19]That little idea with flame on it\n[03:43.22]Not chasing luck, we make it move\n[03:45.25]We make it move, we make it move\n[03:45.89]Yeah\n[03:46.00]I used to say I’m stuck, now I say I’m loading\n[03:47.92]Used to watch the door, now the code is opening\n[03:49.84]Used to call it noise, now I hear the signal\n[03:51.20]Little by little, the vision gets official\n[03:53.36]No more sleepwalking through the sunshine\n[03:57.20]No more waiting for the right time\n[04:00.96]This is the right time, right here\n[04:04.88]Cold drink, clear mind, new gear\n[04:07.60]This summer gon’ be different\n[04:09.76]We ain’t letting it fade away\n[04:13.04]Got the sun on our shoulders\n[04:14.72]Got a brand new game to play\n[04:15.92]This summer gon’ be different\n[04:17.28]No more waiting on someday\n[04:20.64]We gon’ learn a little something\n[04:20.64]We gon’ build our own way\n[04:22.88]Pour it up, let it breathe\n[04:26.18]Palm trees in the fantasy\n[04:28.40]But we working while it glows\n[04:30.24]So the future feels easy\n[04:33.36]This summer gon’ be different\n[04:36.96]Different, different, different\n[04:37.04]This summer gon’ be different\n[04:38.40]And I’m different too\n[04:40.16]Ooh, we been waiting on the light\n[04:46.88]Ooh, we gon’ get it right\n[04:47.68]Ooh, no more losing time\n[04:52.80]This summer, this summer\n[04:54.72]Yeah\n[04:56.56]Same sun\n[04:57.60]New me\n"
